state - of - the - art results.from sentence: As seen , SDNet overpasses all but one baseline models after the second epoch , and achieves state - of - the - art results only after 8 epochs .

achieves.from sentence: As shown , SDNet achieves significantly better results than baseline models .

single SDNet model.from sentence: In detail , the single SDNet model improves overall F 1 by 1.6 % , compared with previous state - of - art model on CoQA , Flow QA .

Ensemble SDNet model.from sentence: Ensemble SDNet model further improves overall F 1 score by 2.7 % , and it 's the first model to achieve over 80 % F 1 score on in - domain datasets ( 80.7 % ) .
